      "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "• Discovery via OSM map-scraping — misses most NBFCs/corporates\n• Silent failures everywhere, zero logging\n• Thin BSE rating data shown as fact\n• No auth, no caching — quota burn + ban risk",
