      "originalText": "• Ingest RBI NBFC list + RBI bank lists + MCA company master\n• companies table in Supabase/Postgres + refresh job\n• Geocode registered addresses once, at ingest\n• /api/search → instant DB query, complete universe\n• BSE / Zauba / Hunter demoted to on-demand enrichment",
